{
  "stem": "4967.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was built for 60 or 70 people, and it must have been 100 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't stand up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to crawl into this place, and it was very hot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were the first night and you could hear explosions, blowing up buildings, shaking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could hear the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the place where I was lying was a little window, but digged into the ground like a basement window, and this was the air was coming in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I see a little box with two wires is pushed into this hole where the window's supposed to be or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I say to my father-- alive then-- I think, dad, they're putting in a box of dynamite, electric one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He looks at this, he say, you're quite right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's dynamite-- electric bomb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, you only have to press a button and it'll explode.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we still lying there a day and a night, and the explosions everywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The demolition squad still didn't manage to come to us, but they put in the bombs wherever the Germans felt, and then the other guys, the other Germans used to come, they detonate and blow it up.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So another night went through, and the explosions from house to house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't hear any noises, only explosions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to go out from this place, because it's dangerous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father was a heavy smoker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I also was a heavy smoker, thanks to the American army who gave me cigarettes in 1945.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] So my father tried to-- tried these matches to light his cigarettes, and it just became blue but it didn't light.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so  a woman, maybe my [INAUDIBLE] tried to light the match.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
